data.description: Location is Everything!!! Seller is offering $5000 towards closing costs!! Nestled within a vibrant community, this stunning home offers a perfect blend of style, functionality, and convenience. As you step inside, you are greeted by an open and airy floor plan that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The primary suite is a retreat within itself, offering serenity and privacy. Additional bedrooms are designed with ample closet space,  large windows and welcoming spaces for family members or guests. Located in a prime location, this modern townhome offers easy access to shopping, dining, entertainment, and transportation options. With its contemporary design, thoughtfully planned layout, and an array of desirable features. Quick Access to City Line, Collin Creek Mall Redevelopment, I75, George Bush Tollway, and DNT. Adjacent to the Greenbelt. Home is East Facing.
